text.section:
The addition under subsection (a) of this section includes the additions required for an individual under:
§ 10-205(b) of this title (Enterprise zone wage credit, employment opportunity credit, disability credit, and qualified ex-felon employee credit);
§ 10-205(c) of this title (Reforestation and timber stand modification);
§ 10-205(e) of this title (Net operating loss modification);
§ 10-205(g) of this title (Unlicensed child care facility operating expenses); and
§ 10-205(i) of this title (Maryland research and development tax credit).
